    <item>
      <title>泰国央行加大力度削减 91% 家庭债务比率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/thai-central-bank-ramps-up-steps-to-cut-91-household-debt-ratio</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国央行正在推出更多措施，确保债务重组成功，以减少约 4540 亿美元的未偿家庭债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/thai-central-bank-ramps-up-steps-to-cut-91-household-debt-ratio</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 08:20:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
